This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as it specifically discusses reproducibility in experimental networking research. It could also potentially belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as these fields often involve experimental research and require reproducibility. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.PF (Performance) as these fields also involve experimental research and require reproducibility.
